        <p>Zomato is one of the largest and most popular platforms for food discovery, ordering, and delivery. Founded in 2008, we aim to make dining out and ordering food easy for everyone. Our goal is to provide a seamless experience for food lovers around the world, connecting you to your favorite restaurants and delivering quality meals right to your doorstep.</p>

